com.foxhole.tools.spartan.managers.resource
Class ResourceManager

java.lang.Object
  com.foxhole.tools.spartan.managers.resource.ResourceManager
All Implemented Interfaces:
ISpartanManager
public class ResourceManager
extends java.lang.Object
implements ISpartanManager

The resource manager enables a simple way to provide resource handles for any part of the game that requests it. Every resource shall be known by an unique identifier that shall be used to obtain the resource. The resource manager can load resources from XML files or they can be added to the resource loader via code.

Author:
Tiago "Spiegel" Costa
